Title: Primum Non Nocere
Plot: Grissom, Catherine and Sara are called in to investigate the death of a hockey player on the ice. Warrick and Nick look into the apparent drug-related death of a sax player at a casino.
GuestStars: Nicole Ari Parker, Jeremy Ratchford, Abby Brammell, Peter MacKenzie, David Andriole, Jeffrey D. Sams, Anthony Dimaria, Dig Wayne
